  <!-- HighlightedPosts Widget ******* -->

  <BlogLatestPosts
    title="Explore More Tech Insights on Our Blog"
    information={`My blog is filled with valuable content covering various aspects of technology, from in-depth tutorials to product reviews and industry insights.
                  Each new article is a step towards mastering the latest in tech trends and tools.
                  Thank you for being a part of my tech journey!`}
  />

  <!-- FAQs Widget ******************* -->

  <FAQs
    title="Frequently Asked Questions"
    subtitle="Explore answers to common questions about Vikshan's YouTube channel and tech content creation."
    tagline="FAQs"
    classes={{ container: 'max-w-6xl' }}
    items={[
      {
        title: "Who is Vikshan's?",
        description:
          "Vikshan is a passionate TechTuber from Africa who shares his knowledge and passion for technology through engaging and informative videos. He's inspired by TechTubers like MKBHD, mrwhosetheboss, JRE, and Hugh Jeffreys.",
      },
      {
        title: 'What topics does Vikshan cover?',
        description:
          'Vikshan covers a wide range of tech topics, including in-depth product reviews, tech tutorials, industry insights, and discussions on the latest tech trends. Stay tuned for diverse and engaging content!',
      },
      {
        title: 'How can I support Vikshan’s channel?',
        description:
          "You can support Vikshan's channel by subscribing, engaging with the content, donating on Ko-Fi, and sharing the videos with friends and fellow tech enthusiasts. Your support means a lot and helps in creating more quality tech content!",
      },
      {
        title: 'What is something that you would like to try again?',
        description:
          "If there's a tech product that you'd like Vikshan to review again or a topic you'd like him to revisit, let him know! Vikshan is always open to new ideas and contributions.",
      },
      {
        title: 'Can I collaborate with Vikshan?',
        description:
          'Vikshan is open to collaborations and partnerships with fellow tech enthusiasts, brands, and organizations. Reach out through the contact information provided on the channel to explore collaboration opportunities!',
      },
      {
        title: 'How often does Vikshan post new videos?',
        description:
          'Vikshan posts new videos every week, ensuring a steady stream of fresh and engaging tech content for viewers. Stay tuned and subscribe to never miss an update!',
      },
    ]}
  />

  <!-- Stats Widget ****************** -->

  <Stats
    stats={[
      { title: 'YT-Subscribers', amount: '600+' },
      { title: 'X Followers', amount: '200+' },
      { title: 'YT-Views', amount: '3K+' },
      { title: 'YT-Videos', amount: '5+' },
    ]}
  />

